title: The Big Valley - Season 2
description:
From Wikipedia:
 The Big Valley is an American western television series which ran on ABC from September 15, 1965, to May 19, 1969. The show stars Barbara Stanwyck, as the widow of a wealthy nineteenth century California rancher. It was created by A.I. Bezzerides and Louis F. Edelman, and produced by Levy-Gardner-Laven for Four Star Television.


 All the previous versions of episodes 16-30 of Season 2 of The Big Valley that I have seen, were lacking in quality. However, I recently found this good quality version on YouTube. The only slight problems with these videos are the black bars on the sides and the fact that I think the aspect ratio should be 2:1. The aspect ratio can quite easily be altered when using VLC Media Player.
